Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.14,0:01:43.47,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,A FEW WEEKS AGO\NAMAZON LILY, ISLAND OF WOMEN
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.44,0:01:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.86,0:01:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a lot of fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.90,0:01:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Walk faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.53,0:01:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Let us go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.95,0:02:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what they'll do to us\Nonce we're taken to the Pirate Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.50,0:02:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect Rayleigh to interrupt,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.71,0:02:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but in the end,\Nwe got some good souvenirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.59,0:02:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vice Admiral, can't we do anything\Nabout our comrades being taken away?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.76,0:02:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we gonna let our men down?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.64,0:02:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't gotten permission from above.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.43,0:02:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're up against an Emperor of the Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.89,0:02:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.48,0:02:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.77,0:02:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to save them?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.24,0:02:44.53,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,JUSTICE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.66,0:02:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Koby!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.37,0:02:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vice Admiral! He's a SWORD member!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.33,0:02:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,SWORD...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.92,0:02:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Koby the Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.84,0:03:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?\NYou want your friends back?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.84,0:03:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't mind an all-out war.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.85,0:03:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're now trying to take away\N800 Navy soldiers and a warship.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.48,0:03:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you let me trade myself\Nfor their release?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.83,0:03:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think very highly of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.20,0:03:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But your life is worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.84,0:03:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lesson one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.63,0:03:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A geezer and a baby are stranded\Non an island full of beasts of prey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.43,0:03:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You rush in to rescue them alone,\Nbut only one other person can fit on that boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.72,0:03:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.35,0:03:52.94,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,FORMER NAVY HQ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.98,0:03:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... First,\NI will get the baby on the boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.31,0:03:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, but then the old man can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.23,0:04:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you waiting for? Hurry up or\Nyou'll all get killed and devoured.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.61,0:04:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.53,0:04:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.11,0:04:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I'll get off the boat\Nand let the old man and the baby on board!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.37,0:04:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then they'll both...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.91,0:04:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.00,0:04:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.71,0:04:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.00,0:04:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gee. Remember this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.13,0:04:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The geezer only has\Na short time ahead of him...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.93,0:04:25.26,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,TA-DAH!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.22,0:04:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So abandon him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.68,0:04:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.30,0:04:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Vice Admiral Garp!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.60,0:04:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you guys join the Navy to save?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.48,0:04:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.57,0:04:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...did you guys join the Navy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.78,0:04:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to save?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.32,0:04:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"The Last Lesson!\NImpact Inherited"{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.67,0:04:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.30,0:05:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.46,0:05:07.55,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,PRESENT DAY, PIRATE ISLAND OF BEEHIVE
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.86,0:05:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot! Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.79,0:05:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cannonfire does nothing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.92,0:05:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.54,0:05:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Full speed ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.25,0:05:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna let you escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.84,0:05:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What terrifying power...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.48,0:05:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If a huge hand like that\Ncomes down on them,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.52,0:06:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,hundreds of soldiers and civilians\Nwill die!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.19,0:06:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible! We can't stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.65,0:06:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to dive into the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.45,0:06:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those inside, go on deck\Nand protect the civilians!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.12,0:06:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.87,0:06:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's going to die because of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.92,0:06:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Was I wrong in my decision?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.84,0:06:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I haven't saved anyone yet!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.47,0:06:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't save anyone!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.77,0:06:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What should I...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.28,0:06:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What should I do?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.28,0:06:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys can...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.79,0:06:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...save them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.83,0:07:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vice Admiral Garp!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.34,0:07:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.97,0:07:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.93,0:07:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll create an opening!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.47,0:07:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, Captain Koby...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.23,0:07:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Destroy the island monster's hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.02,0:07:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! How can I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.52,0:07:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rear Admiral Grus, protect the ship\Nfrom the debris of the hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.45,0:07:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant Commander Helmeppo,\Ndon't let anyone stand in the way of those two!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.41,0:07:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.99,0:07:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vice Admiral Garp! But that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.83,0:07:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Decisions must always be\Nmade in an instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.50,0:07:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.72,0:07:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.81,0:08:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Koby and the others are on the move!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.86,0:08:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use! What can you do without Garp?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.03,0:08:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll all be sunk into the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.24,0:08:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There they come!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.20,0:08:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Helmeppo! Take care of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.08,0:08:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.12,0:08:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You heard what Vice Admiral Garp said!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.04,0:08:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Why is it always me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.25,0:08:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.75,0:08:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's too many!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.05,0:08:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too many! Oh, too many!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.17,0:08:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Koby! He told you to destroy it.\NDo you have a bomb or something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.30,0:08:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't!\NBut I gotta figure something out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.10,0:08:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Figure something out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.56,0:08:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's big enough to hold\Nand crush a warship!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.35,0:08:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.73,0:08:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you escape, Koby!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.61,0:08:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.03,0:08:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Koby!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.99,0:09:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let anyone stand in the way of those two!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.66,0:09:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.75,0:09:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll leave you...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.63,0:09:09.25,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,CHORE BOY
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.25,0:09:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...the rest!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.13,0:09:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.63,0:09:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Helmeppo-{\i1}san{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.30,0:09:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look back, Koby!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.47,0:09:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--But...\N--You gotta keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.98,0:09:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.11,0:09:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Garp-{\i1}san{\i}, where do you think you're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.95,0:09:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're heavily injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.20,0:09:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just a scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.75,0:09:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried about you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.88,0:09:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too soft!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.04,0:10:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Garp! Why is he coming this way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.13,0:10:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Don't you care\Nwhat'll happen to the ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.80,0:10:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Galaxy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.42,0:10:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Divide!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.67,0:11:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The arm is recoiling!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.77,0:11:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is what he meant by an "opening"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.56,0:11:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That made the arm go up!\NWhat are you gonna do, Koby?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.53,0:11:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vice Admiral... Garp!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.24,0:11:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why?! I'm not worthy enough to save...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.87,0:11:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Koby is the future of the Navy!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.42,0:11:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't disappoint you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.38,0:12:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Koby!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.22,0:12:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.27,0:12:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not enough to stop me, Garp!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.69,0:12:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really pissed off-{\i1}meow{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.48,0:12:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch closely!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.99,0:12:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As your men die!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.16,0:12:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill them all-{\i1}meow{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.16,0:12:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.12,0:12:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't save them in time-{\i1}meow{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.21,0:12:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, Helmeppo.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.04,0:12:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Koby progresses quickly\Nbut is often injured.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.47,0:12:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Koby's injury...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.38,0:12:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... He told me not to tell you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.23,0:13:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not as good a fighter as the others,\Nso 10 times isn't enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.44,0:13:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to train myself 100 times\Nor 200 times harder than them...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.16,0:13:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to be a good Navy soldier\Nwho can protect someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.21,0:13:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.80,0:13:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.42,0:13:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to stop now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.84,0:13:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy... So he's been training by himself\Non top of my training?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.35,0:13:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he's been doing it every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.06,0:13:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Punching the Battleship Bag...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.57,0:13:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...with his fists...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.86,0:13:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...covered in blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.62,0:13:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gotta make it in time!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.67,0:14:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gotta make it!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.42,0:14:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gotta make it!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.51,0:14:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I gotta make it in time!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.23,0:14:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.86,0:14:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Koby-{\i1}senpai{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.03,0:14:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Koby!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.91,0:14:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! It's Koby!\NIs he trying to stop the hand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.04,0:14:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.62,0:14:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's like an ant to that hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.92,0:14:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People call him the Hero,\Nso that stupid brat is pushing his luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.59,0:14:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Koby-{\i1}senpai{\i}! It's dangerous up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.96,0:14:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get away, Koby-{\i1}kun{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.68,0:14:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch as the ship gets smashed\Nand the soldiers scream as they die!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.89,0:15:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if they dive into the sea,\NAokiji will freeze them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.19,0:15:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Serves you right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.20,0:15:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}People will die because of me.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.04,0:15:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I gotta destroy it!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.04,0:15:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I don't, they'll all die!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.67,0:15:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm not as good a fighter as the others,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.30,0:15:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so 10 times isn't enough!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.56,0:15:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to train myself 100 times\Nor 200 times harder than them!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.69,0:15:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What did you guys join the Navy to save?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.95,0:15:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Koby!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.36,0:15:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too late! Abandon ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.99,0:16:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You guys can save them!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.09,0:16:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honesty...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.30,0:16:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Impact!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.28,0:17:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did he gain such a power?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.33,0:17:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.79,0:17:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what should we do about the debris?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.38,0:17:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect the ship from the debris!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.72,0:17:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Glorp Web!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.85,0:17:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Koby!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.15,0:17:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Koby! I can't believe you did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.15,0:17:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Helmeppo-{\i1}san{\i}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.03,0:17:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.79,0:18:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.29,0:18:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.92,0:18:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You broke that huge mountain of an arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.01,0:18:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home, you fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.60,0:18:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Koby!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.14,0:18:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Helmeppo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.65,0:18:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad that you're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.06,0:18:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Koby-{\i1}senpai{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.28,0:18:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hibari-{\i1}san{\i}...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.49,0:18:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.32,0:18:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.87,0:18:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now all we need to do is\Nget Vice Admiral Garp on board and go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.41,0:18:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ring, ring, ring... Ring, ring, ring...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.88,0:18:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clank.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.17,0:18:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is Garp.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.92,0:18:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The mission to rescue Captain Koby\Nis complete.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.30,0:19:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vice Admiral Garp!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.89,0:19:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.18,0:19:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and come back to the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.68,0:19:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.22,0:19:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...go ahead and leave Beehive.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.31,0:19:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.19,0:19:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about, Garp-{\i1}san{\i}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.32,0:19:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.69,0:19:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The top priority is the safety of you all.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.82,0:19:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Am I right?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.87,0:19:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.12,0:19:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prince, turn the ship around...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.54,0:19:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our success here...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.09,0:19:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...will pose a threat to all pirates.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.10,0:19:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me join the Navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.72,0:19:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy to do odd jobs or anything like that\Nif I can become a Navy soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.19,0:19:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you guys join the Navy to save?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.48,0:20:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the future of the people, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.40,0:20:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, you guys got\Nmore time to live than a geezer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.58,0:20:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take the baby...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.79,0:20:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and live on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.02,0:20:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Keep going.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.89,0:20:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You guys are the future...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.31,0:20:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...of the Navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.15,0:20:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clank.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.87,0:20:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vice Admiral Garp!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.70,0:20:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ever give a lecture like that!\NAll lives are equal!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.04,0:20:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The future of the young people\Nis limitless!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.06,0:21:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The next day, newspapers reported...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.93,0:21:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...the survival of the young naval hero,\NCaptain Koby,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.56,0:21:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the disappearance of Vice Admiral Garp,\Nthe Legendary Hero, on the Pirate Island,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.36,0:21:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and the Emperor of the Sea,\NStraw Hat Luffy, barricading himself...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.62,0:21:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...on the Future Island Egghead.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.91,0:21:39.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,STRAW HATS
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.05,0:21:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How far I have run{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.05,0:21:51.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}doredake hashitte kita noka{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.89,0:21:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Without knowing it, I counted scars{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.89,0:21:58.48,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}wakaranai mama kizuato kazoeta{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.94,0:22:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A treasure map in my head all along{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.94,0:22:05.90,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}zutto atama no naka ni aru takara no chizu{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.95,0:22:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Still looking for the future{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.95,0:22:12.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}mirai wo sagashi tsuzuketeru{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.45,0:22:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The real promise{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.45,0:22:19.12,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}hontou no yakusoku wa{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.17,0:22:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lies much deeper in my heart{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.17,0:22:26.30,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}mune no oku no motto oku ni aru{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.34,0:22:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A dream that no one can catch up with{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.34,0:22:35.43,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}dare mo mina oitsukenai yume{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.47,0:22:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's all I hold on to{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.47,0:22:41.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}tada hitotsu dakishimete{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.19,0:22:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To you who smiles like the sun{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.19,0:22:48.24,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}taiyou no youni warau anata e{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.28,0:22:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll sing the same song as that day{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.28,0:22:55.16,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}ano hi to onaji uta wo utau yo{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.20,0:23:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This wish I don't want to forget even when I grow up{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.20,0:23:02.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}otona ni nattemo wasuretakunai{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.25,0:23:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Until it reaches you{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.25,0:23:09.68,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}kono negai ga todoku made{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.77,0:23:18.35,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ORIGINAL STORY BY EIICHIRO ODA\NWEEKLY SHONEN JUMP (SHUEISHA) SERIES
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.52,0:23:19.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ORIGINAL CONCEPT BY TOMOHITO OSAKI\NTHE STRAW HAT STORIES
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.27,0:23:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dear Nami{\i1}-san{\i},\Nplease keep having wonderful adventures!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.16,0:23:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hat Crew\Nreunites at Sabaody Archipelago today!